### Question API Test
# This file contains HTTP requests for testing the Question API endpoints.
# It demonstrates how to create, read, update, and delete questions.

### Create a new question
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/questions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

{
  "title": "What is Kotlin?",
  "content": "Can someone explain what Kotlin is and its main features?",
  "tags": ["kotlin", "programming"]
}

