### Update a question
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/questions/question_id
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

{
  "title": "What is Kotlin and why use it?",
  "content": "Can someone explain what Kotlin is, its main features, and why it's preferred over Java?",
  "tags": ["kotlin", "programming", "java"]
}

